There is some code that will be never executed in the gtk_misc_set_padding and gtk_misc_set_alignment methods.

The code was found in gtk+-2.11.6/gtk/gtkmisc.c

Here's a snipped and I think no more words are necessary. The same thing should be fixed in gtk_misc_set_padding.

  if ((xalign != misc->xalign) || (yalign != misc->yalign))
    {
      misc->xalign = xalign // <--- THIS
      misc->yalign = yalign

      // cut

      g_object_freeze_notify (G_OBJECT (misc))
      if (xalign != misc->xalign) // <--- AND THIS
	g_object_notify (G_OBJECT (misc) xalign)

      if (yalign != misc->yalign)
